00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,100
 nekako odgovornost za ovu zajednicu.

223
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:27,440
 Samo je ovdje jedna politička zajednica

224
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,460
 koja se zove Hrvatska.

225
00:14:28,460 --> 00:14:30,140
 I odgovornost je zapravo,

226
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:31,120
 naravno,

227
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,180
 nije država samo nekako

228
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:34,920
 neko ko pruža neke usluge.

229
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:36,440
 Kao država je sad tu neke,

230
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:38,180
 ona treba pružati neke usluge,

231
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,740
 rješavati neke, ne znam i ja,

232
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:41,220
 komunalne probleme

233
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,800
 ili infrastrukturne probleme.

234
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,520
 Ne, ona je tu zapravo upravo to

235
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:46,460
 da omogući opstanak

236
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:47,880
 i održavanje jedne zajednice,

237
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:48,440
 jednog naroda.

238
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,160
 Jednog naroda,

239
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,400
 koje zove Hrvatski narod.

240
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:52,300
 Znači, to je funkcija države,

241
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:52,580
 kažem,

242
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:54,040
 a ne sad zapravo samo

243
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:55,040
 da ona ima konkurent.

244
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,920
 Ok, ja znam da je važno

245
00:14:56,920 --> 00:14:58,480
 da je država globalno konkurenta,

246
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,760
 ali ne može funkcija države

247
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:01,380
 biti globalna konkurentnost.

248
00:15:01,380 --> 00:15:01,900
 Nadavno.

249
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:02,940
 Ne možemo mi samo gledati

250
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,040
 nekakve ljestvice

251
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:07,320
 ili rangove globalne konkurentnosti.

252
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,640
 Ja znam da je to danas neophodno

253
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:09,900
 u ovom otvorenom ekonomski

254
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:12,540
 svijetu kojem živa,

255
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:13,260
 ali zapravo to je to.

256
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:14,920
 Država je tu da osigura

257
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:16,440
 opstanak i razvoj zajednice.

258
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,580
 Ali ta konkurentnost globalna,

259
00:15:18,580 --> 00:15:19,900
 to je alat,

260
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:21,520
 to je sredstvo da ta zajednica

261
00:15:21,520 --> 00:15:22,100
 opstane,

262
00:15:22,100 --> 00:15:23,740
 a ne cilj samo po sebi.

263
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:25,280
 A s druge strane,

264
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:28,120
 kada ti gaš otvoreno,

265
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,080
 mi smo sve otvorenije,

266
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:31,560
 onda zvuči kao da bi mi,

267
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,720
 kao da bi željeli

268
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,000
 da mi budemo zatvoreni.

269
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,940
 Ne, ali postoje otvorenost

