 Znači,

308
00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:17,480
 svi žele zapravo ratiti

309
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:18,160
 te nekakve,

310
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:19,020
 zapravo,

311
