 ove poslove

312
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,960
 visoko obrazovane,

313
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:23,100
 svi žele biti,

314
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:23,620
 znači,

315
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:24,660
 profesionalci,

316
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:25,500
 visoko plaćeni,

