 te ekonomije treba,

332
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:43,140
 ona njih privlači,

333
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:44,240
 i to je ta ideja.

334
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,040
 Ovo je sve zapravo,

335
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:46,200
 ja bih rekao,

336
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,760
 kako bih rekao,

