 uspiju doći do Krvatske.

375
00:17:28,780 --> 00:17:29,160
 Naravno.

376
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,360
 Zato im je netko gore

377
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:31,240
 na sjeveru,

378
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,020
 drugim državama

