426
00:18:24,380 --> 00:18:25,600
 uopće ne razgovara.

427
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:26,200
 Pa mi smo,

428
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:26,460
 ja mislim,

429
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:27,280
 taj najveći odljev

430
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:32,600
 koji se tu nije mogao

431
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:34,480
 snaći,

432
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:36,380
 koji nije imao neku,

433
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,360
 možemo reći tu,

434
00:18:37,360 --> 00:18:40,240
 kako je rekao?

435
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,200
 Vezu.

436
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,640
 Čak i vezu,

437
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,820
 ali zapravo nije imao nešto

438
00:18:43,820 --> 00:18:45,260
 da to može nekako amortizirati.

439
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:46,260
 Nije mogao imati neki

440
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,860
 socijalni amortizir

441
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:48,840
 kod obitelji,

442
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,620
 kod nekakvog,

443
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:50,220
 ja možemo reći,

444
00:18:50,220 --> 00:18:52,040
 kruga kojem je pripadao

445
00:18:52,040 --> 00:18:52,860
 i ti ljudi su otišti.

446
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:53,140
 Jan dio,

447
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:54,260
 normalno ljudi traži

448
00:18:54,260 --> 00:18:55,180
 bolje prilike,

449
00:18:55,180 --> 00:18:56,200
 to je jasno,

450
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:56,800
 ali je,

451
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,400
 činjenica je

452
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,320
 da smo mi zapravo imali

453
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:59,520
 jedan veliki odljev ljudi

454
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,640
 koji je otišao,

455
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:01,500
 a sad,

456
00:19:01,500 --> 00:19:02,380
 je li sad tražimo

457
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:02,940
 ovaj,

458
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:04,040
 ali mi kaže,

459
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:04,740
 ono što nama...

460
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:05,700
 Da tražimo rješenja

461
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:06,480
 da se oni vrate.

462
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,040
 Ali kaže,

463
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:08,660
 mi tražimo zapravo rješenja,

464
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:09,100
 kao što vidite,

465
00:19:09,100 --> 00:19:10,760
 mi ne uvozimo mi sad nekakve,

466
00:19:10,760 --> 00:19:11,440
 to je vrlo malo,

467
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:12,520
 ne uvozimo mi sad nekakve

468
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:14,160
 visoko obrazovane stručnjake

469
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:15,040
 ili profesionalce.

470
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:16,680
 Nama zapravo trebaju ljudi,

471
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:17,020
 ne znam,

472
00:19:17,020 --> 00:19:18,220
 za koji će se,

473
00:19:18,220 --> 00:19:18,500
 na primjer,

474
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,340
 starati i brinuti

475
00:19:19,340 --> 00:19:20,800
 o starijim nemoćnim ljudima,

476
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:21,500
 nama ljudi trebaju

477
00:19:21,500 --> 00:19:22,180
 za dostavu

478
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:23,140
 koju će dostavljati,

479
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:24,260
 nama ljudi trebaju

480
00:19:24,260 --> 00:19:25,440
 za koji će raditi

481
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:26,940
 u hotelijestu

482
00:19:26,940 --> 00:19:27,520
 i općen to tim

483
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:28,700
 usluženim djelatnosti,

484
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:29,480
 ima tu nešto

485
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,400
 i u industriji,

486
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:30,900
 ali ne toliko,

487
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:32,080
 znači trebaju nam ljudi

488
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:32,400
 za ono,

489
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,220
 za te zapravo,

490
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,000
 ono što se,

491
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:36,480
 te nisko kvalificirane

492
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:37,260
 zapravo poslove,

493
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:38,320
 jednostavne...

494
00:19:38,320 --> 00:19:39,120
 Ali s druge strane,

495
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,400
 kad govorimo o ovoj njezi,

496
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,860
 o jedan segment odljeva,

497
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:44,220
 su ljudi Hrvati

498
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:45,220
 koji odlazi iz Hrvatske

499
00:19:45,220 --> 00:19:45,960
 da bi te poslove

500
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,340
 obavljali u drugim državama,

501
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:48,560
 iste te poslove,

502
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:49,680
 zato da su bolje plaći.

503
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:50,500
 Tako je, upravo to.

504
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:51,160
 Ali to je ta,

505
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,500
 zato mislim da,

506
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:54,180
 zato taj stalni protok

507
00:19:54,180 --> 00:19:55,460
 i dolazak strane radne snage

508
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:56,600
 nekim ljudima odgovara.

509
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,320
 Jer pazite,

510
00:19:57,320 --> 00:19:58,260
 naprimjer te Hrvati,

511
00:19:58,260 --> 00:19:59,020
 to je ta tradicija,

512
00:19:59,020 --> 00:19:59,320
 ja mislim,

513
00:19:59,320 --> 00:20:00,240
 batante, te žene

514
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,240
 koje višle u Italiju

515
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:01,640
 čuvati,

516
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,460
 starije ljude,

517
00:20:02,460 --> 00:20:04,720
 zapravo oni su njih plaćali

518
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:05,440
 jer su njih mogli

519
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,520
 priuštiti za razliku

520
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:07,120
 od Talijanki.

521
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,140
 Tako i sad.

522
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,120
 Realno dobar dio ljudi

523
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:11,020
 u Hrvatskoj će pozdraviti,

524
00:20:11,020 --> 00:20:11,400
 naprimjer,

525
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,360
 sad da dolaze žene

526
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:13,300
 iz Filipina,

527
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:13,800
 Nepala,

528
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:15,620
 da čuvaju starije ljude

529
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:16,940
 jer njih mogu priuštiti.

530
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:17,940
 I to je,

531
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:18,980
 i realno postoji

532
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:19,980
 taj jedna ekonomska računica

533
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:21,060
 i nekim ljudima odgovara.

534
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:21,720
 Kako je ona ima

535
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:22,980
 posljedice za nas

536
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:23,620
 kao društvo?

537
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:24,120
 Upravo to.

538
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:25,480
 Mi se bitno mijenjamo

539
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,060
 kao društvo,

540
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:26,720
 to je jasno.

541
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:28,580
 Sve je više.

542
00:20:28,580 --> 00:20:30,220
 Ono što se nama nameće,

543
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:30,940
 po meni krivo,

544
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:32,260
 je da je zapravo

545
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:33,520
 multikulturalizam

546
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:34,360
 jedna blagostanje

547
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:34,840
 i blagostvo.

548
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:35,400
 On to nije.

549
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,740
 Definitivno on nije.

550
00:20:36,740 --> 00:20:38,200
 Ja razumijem

551
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,720
 da je on jednostavno

552
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:40,180
 dobrim,

553
00:20:40,180 --> 00:20:40,460
 mislim,

554
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:40,960
 mi smo uvijek bile

555
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:41,820
 raznoliko društvo.

556
00:20:41,820 --> 00:20:42,700
 Znači Hrvatska je uvijek

557
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:44,840
 bilo i kulturno raznoliko

558
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,740
 i heterogeno društvo,

559
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:46,720
 ali sad se to baš

560
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,420
 kao nameće,

561
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:48,100
 vi ako čitate,

562
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:48,380
 ne znam,

563
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,320
 na primjer komentatore

564
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:51,180
 u našim mainstream medijima,

565
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:52,040
 zapravo to,

566
00:20:52,040 --> 00:20:53,040
 ko se ne slaže

567
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:53,680
 s ton idejom

568
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:54,280
 da treba biti

569
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:55,060
 što više stranaca

570
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:01,920
 istraživanje

571
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:02,600
 onog najpoznatijih

572
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:03,520
 svjetskih politologa

573
00:21:03,520 --> 00:21:04,360
 Roberta Patnama

574
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:05,060
 kojom je radio tamo

575
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:06,200
 negdje sredinom 90-ih,

576
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,260
 gdje je zapravo

577
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,100
 pronašao u Americi

578
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:08,940
 što je zajednica

579
00:21:08,940 --> 00:21:10,820
 rasno kulturna raznolikija,

580
00:21:10,820 --> 00:21:11,640
 to je manje

581
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,800
 socijalno povjerenje,

582
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:14,360
 to je manje solidarnosti

583
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:14,940
 među ljudima,

584
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:16,060
 zapravo kohezije

585
00:21:16,060 --> 00:21:17,120
 manje u društvu.

586
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:18,420
 Znači i nepovjerenje

587
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:19,020
 ne pada samo

588
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:19,880
 između pripadnika

589
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,820
 različitih zajednica,

590
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:21,420
 nego i općento

591
00:21:21,420 --> 00:21:22,380
 između iste zajednice

592
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:24,060
 jednostavno povjerenje.

593
00:21:24,060 --> 00:21:25,080
 Ali to je veza,

594
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:25,760
 to je potpuno,

595
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,480
 ovo što je Patnama postavio,

596
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,740
 je potpuno logično.

597
00:21:29,740 --> 00:21:31,460
 Jer ti s čovjekom

598
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,220
 kojim si ti,

599
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:33,280
 cilje kohezije,

600
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:34,160
 jedinstvo je cilj,

601
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,580
 odnosno da mi što bolje

602
00:21:35,580 --> 00:21:36,420
 jedni drugi razumijemo.

603
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:36,700
 Tako je, da.

604
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:38,440
 Tako, ako ja čovjeka

605
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:40,080
 koji gledam preko puta sebe,

606
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,580
 ja sam neki dan sjedela u tramvu

607
00:21:41,580 --> 00:21:43,240
 i gledam jedan simpatičan

608
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:45,060
 mladi čovjek stranac

609
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:46,060
 koji ovdje očito radi,

610
00:21:46,060 --> 00:21:47,220
 ja sad njega gledam,

611
00:21:47,220 --> 00:21:48,440
 ja se mislim da na njegovom mjestu

612
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:50,720
 sjedi jedan dečko iz Zagreba.

613
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,780
 Ja za njega,

614
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:53,420
 na pet osnovnih pitanjima

615
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:53,960
 o tome gdje,

616
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,220
 što on misli o nečemu,

617
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,380
 bi znala dati

618
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,580
 dosta dobru procenu.

619
00:21:57,580 --> 00:21:58,500
 Ja za ovog čovjeka

620
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,060
 uopće ništa ne znam.

621
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:02,200
 Ja ne znam kako on reagira

622
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,160
 na određene stvari,

623
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,580
 koja je vjerojatnost

624
00:22:04,580 --> 00:22:05,980
 da će reagirat na određen način.

625
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:06,240
 Dakle,

626
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:08,100
 to je jednostavno nepoznavanje

627
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:09,280
 uz puno poštovanje

628
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:10,560
 njegovog dostojanstva

629
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:11,460
 i tko je on.

630
00:22:11,460 --> 00:22:12,740
 Mislim, to je ko kad mi odemo

631
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,660
 u Nepal u konačnicu.

632
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:15,920
 I sva istraživanja

633
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,560
 ipak pokazuju

634
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:17,640
 da su ljudi prvenstveno

635
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:19,120
 usmjereni najviše

636
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:20,140
 ipak na svoju zajednicu.

637
00:22:20,140 --> 00:22:21,780
 Znači nije to samo u Hrvatsku,

638
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:22,680
 tako i u Nizemsku.

639
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,400
 Tako je među onih

640
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,820
 najkozmopolitskim nacijama,

641
00:22:24,820 --> 00:22:25,880
 koje je.

642
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:26,960
 One su usmjerene

643
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:27,800
 i prema svijetu,

644
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:29,060
 stalo in je do svijeta,

645
00:22:29,060 --> 00:22:29,860
 ali su nekako ipak

646
00:22:29,860 --> 00:22:31,180
 i dalje dominantno usmjerene

647
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,380
 na svoju zajednicu.

648
00:22:32,380 --> 00:22:33,900
 Upućene su na svoje ljude i ljudi.

649
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,120
 Ali naravno kažen,

650
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,340
 ipak su tu jake snage,

651
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:37,580
 to treba reći,

652
00:22:37,580 --> 00:22:39,040
 ipak su tu jake, jake snage,

653
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:40,960
 globalne i prvenstveno ekonomske,

654
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:43,200
 koje je zapravo na neki način

655
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,020
 žele ukidanje svih mogućih granica

656
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:46,740
 i da se mi zapravo pretvorimo

657
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:47,360
 u neku vrstu,

658
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:47,860
 ja bih rekao,

659
00:22:47,860 --> 00:22:50,000
 permisivnog potrošaškog pojedinca.

660
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:53,080
 Da se lišimo svi ti nekih identiteta

661
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:54,420
 pripadnosti zajednici,

662
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:56,120
 osim određenih identiteta,

663
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:56,840
 ti mogu obstat,

664
00:22:56,840 --> 00:22:58,820
 ali zapravo nacionalnog identiteta,

665
00:22:58,820 --> 00:22:59,920
 zavičaja i tako dalje,

666
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,700
 ideja je,

667
00:23:00,700 --> 00:23:03,960
 jer onda zapravo taj globalni kapital

668
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:04,800
 može lako,

669
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:06,980
 ako vi nate identiteta,

670
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,320
 vi onda ne želite možda

671
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:10,600
 kupiti neki proizvod vaše zemlje,

672
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:12,700
 otići u neko vaše turičiško odredište,

673
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:13,980
 nego je ideja.

674
00:23:13,980 --> 00:23:16,820
 Ne želite jačati svog čovjeka

675
00:23:16,820 --> 00:23:18,380
 koji proizvodi nešto u Hrvatskoj,

676
00:23:18,380 --> 00:23:20,520
 nema te osjeće odgovornosti za njega.

677
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:21,560
 Vi ste potrošač,

678
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:23,120
 vi niste više pripadnik neke zajednice,

679
00:23:23,120 --> 00:23:23,960
 nego s tobrišan potrošač.

680
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:24,980
 Samo to, tako je,

681
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:25,920
 to je glavna karakteristika.

682
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:26,220
 Da, to je to.

683
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:27,740
 I u principu to predstavlja,

684
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:30,680
 u sve drugo predstavlja jedno osiromašenje.

685
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:33,060
 Da će se oduzima ta tvoja boja,

686
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:33,900
 tvoj kolorit.

687
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:35,440
 Naravno da će rast nejednakosti,

688
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,560
 jer uvijek će biti neki jači

689
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:37,660
 koji će dominirati.

690
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,140
 To je to.

691
00:23:38,140 --> 00:23:40,380
 Kaže, mi zapravo imamo tu ideju

692
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:42,940
 iz ostanka brige i odgovornosti

693
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,660
 za zajednicu.

694
00:23:43,660 --> 00:23:45,360
 I nažalost, ono što se nama nameće

695
